#!/usr/bin/env python
"""
CESMLC V9 - reference-safe problem-state model trainer
======================================================

Recommended input:
  cesmlc_v9_balanced_model_ready_training_dataset.csv
or:
  cesmlc_v8_2_balanced_model_ready_training_dataset.csv

Key fixes:
* Excludes REFERENCE_/DATA_SOURCE_/RCA fields from model features.
* Excludes FEATURE_EVIDENCE_SCORE / FEATURE_EVIDENCE_PERCENTILE and all seed/rule/report fields.
* Saves each backend under its own output folder: <out-dir>/<backend>/...
* Produces per-class quality reports and problem-only plots.
"""
